# PostPilot frontend — environment variables
#
# No environment variables are required for the frontend.
# The Vite dev server proxies all /api requests to http://localhost:8000 via vite.config.js.
#
# If you deploy the frontend separately from the backend, set VITE_API_URL
# to your backend's public URL and update vite.config.js accordingly.
#
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend.example.com
